df17dc10-e8e9-5044-8979-8b2d2d332b9e,tg:rubgr:661,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"[recto] Ad [Addendum] Flight into Egypt. The falling idol, falling from a way side shrine attached to a tree, like in A.S. picture, but the tree placed on the left border in Lucas Gassel's 'Flight into Egypt', dated 1542 (formerly in S. de Schrijver coll. Brussels, in 1940 on Amsterdam market.  See S. [Simon] de Schrijver, Lucas Gassel, peintre paysagiste du XVIe S., in: Annales de la Société d'Archéologie de Bruxelles, V, 1891, p. 379-80), [kantlijn] Mentioned ders Friedländer Essays [= Essays über die Landschaftsmalerei und andere Bildgattungen, Den Haag: Stols], 1947, p. 72), discussed and repr. by F.S.E. BAUDOUIN, [Een landschap van Lucas Gassel te München], in Oud-Holland, LXV, 1950, [pp. 151-158], p. 153, Auch sonst Ähnlichkeiten wichtig!!; [verso] The same also in Ysenbrant, Flight into Egypt, formerly in Thiem Coll. now New York, Robert T. Francis Coll. (repr. Baldass, Jb. 1918).",descriptive note,Nederlands,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

column4: <content>[recto] Ad [Addendum] Flight into Egypt. The falling idol, falling from a way side shrine attached to a tree, like in A.S. picture, but the tree placed on the left border in Lucas Gassel's 'Flight into Egypt', dated 1542 (formerly in S. de Schrijver coll. Brussels, in 1940 on Amsterdam market.  See S. [Simon] de Schrijver, Lucas Gassel, peintre paysagiste du XVIe S., in: Annales de la Société d'Archéologie de Bruxelles, V, 1891, p. 379-80), [kantlijn] Mentioned ders Friedländer Essays [= Essays über die Landschaftsmalerei und andere Bildgattungen, Den Haag: Stols], 1947, p. 72), discussed and repr. by F.S.E. BAUDOUIN, [Een landschap van Lucas Gassel te München], in Oud-Holland, LXV, 1950, [pp. 151-158], p. 153, Auch sonst Ähnlichkeiten wichtig!!; [verso] The same also in Ysenbrant, Flight into Egypt, formerly in Thiem Coll. now New York, Robert T. Francis Coll. (repr. Baldass, Jb. 1918).</content>
